{"tid":1215770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我懷疑尋日已經有人死咗，政府會唔會隱瞞死左人？","createTime":"2019-06-13T08:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T02:15:17.000Z","uid":43785,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ace84ed0035d67d612c55d413e31bd0be750a84","tid":1215770,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"好多傷者冇公佈<br />\n好多嚴重嘅傷者冇公佈<br />\n<br />\n尋日晏晝睇到篇文話有個傷者入咗嚟已經死咗， 雖然未知真假，<br />\n但傳媒真係好鬼，完全冇公佈到傷者情況， 可能驚有第一個人死咗留咗第一滴血之後就會引起更多人彈出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n尋日明明嘔血嗰個人好大鑊， 又有人爆眼， 有個女人畀人向頭開槍， 又有女人畀人㩒喺地下俾班黑警磨擦......<br />\n<br />\n我想問呢班人去曬邊度，冇一個人有報到平安？<br />\n究竟係已經重傷不治，定係警察拉咗？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有消息可以公佈下？"},{"pid":"c9e53c5788c28fc9df48c024468e547f169df2e2","tid":1215770,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"未死但可能比人滅聲？<br />\n<br />\n以告唔告作籌碼？"},{"pid":"cd01dc11f70e3df77b8db30d7f9be07a2ce50729","tid":1215770,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9e53c5788c28fc9df48c024468e547f169df2e2","tid":1215770,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"未死但可能比人滅聲？<br />\n<br />\n以告唔告作籌碼？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70fbddfbc3c5fd8f90c38f7fdb5311d0e4463ce","tid":1215770,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"鳩sir,過左咁耐，可唔可以透露下你知道既情報有幾多？"}]}